WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.480
Shah Rukh Khan: Everyone wants to know
what tomorrow,

00:00:05.480 --> 00:00:08.480
the next month or the next year 
holds for them.

00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:12.160
Joining us from London, 
our speaker Anab Jain is of the opinion

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:17.870
that we do not need any soothsayers 
to tell us about our future,

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:22.520
we just need to look 
at our world today more closely.

00:00:22.520 --> 00:00:24.400
On TED Talks India Nayi Soch

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.700
to give us today a glimpse 
into tomorrow's world,

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:28.070
we have with us today

00:00:28.088 --> 00:00:29.918
the multi-talented designer,
filmmaker, inventor ...

00:00:29.938 --> 00:00:32.688
please welcome on stage, Anab Jain.